msgctxt "Talk01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I've been all over the world, but this\n"
"place is truly the hottest of them all.\n"
"I'd die here without a <2.se_co>fireproof elixir<3.re_co>.\n"
"Yeah, I'm not sure I'll be able to draw\n"
"anything here... So I'll just burn this\n"
"scenery into my memory."
